Problem Statement:
Best Stuff - Cheap Stuff, Buy Buy Buy... Store Instance: source. The shop is open for business at nc mercury.picoctf.net 10337.

Points: 50

Hints:
1. Always check edge cases when programming

Solution:
use netcat in your terminal 
nc mercury.picoctf.net 10337

Buy negative number of apples 
Use the money got to buy the fruitful flag.
The list of numbers we get can be converted to text using an ASCII to text converter (https://codebeautify.org/ascii-to-text)

Flag:
https://codebeautify.org/ascii-to-text
